\v 11 He said these things, and after that, he said to them, \wj “\+w Our\+w* \+w friend\+w* \+w Lazarus\+w* \+w has\+w* \+w fallen\+w* \+w asleep\+w*, \+w but\+w* \+w I\+w* \+w am\+w* \+w going\+w* \+w so\+w* \+w that\+w* \+w I\+w* \+w may\+w* awake \+w him\+w* \+w out\+w* \+w of\+w* \+w sleep\+w*.”\wj* 
\p
